e6837598","tid":2263377,"uid":313615,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T00:35:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><br />\n一個星期後，徐永權氣急敗壞地打來電話，他終於發現自己被媒體曝光，徐永權氣急敗壞大罵古懿：&ldquo;你這個人太壞了&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n後來古懿聽說，徐永權已經不做國保了，在當地開了一家牛肉湯店。<br />\n</strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T03:08:57.000Z","msg":"这个坏人就是本人。徐永权改行卖牛肉的消息来自当地政府，因为他的饭店太脏被处罚了。"},{"pid":"2d4a7cc8d58668e24c38af29efd582d555431263","tid":2263377,"uid":236003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3bf87abc9ee1f77d7c4afb6daf279c73870e3fcd","tid":2263377,"uid":151074,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T00:55:52.000Z","msg":"每日都岀呢啲post, translate做英文俾白廢睇下自己最愛嘅China係乜東東<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T06:40:22.000Z","msg":"睇唔到㗎佢哋，未俾人打過佢哋會繼續覺得中国係共產主義天堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}